headline.main: Saudi to Overhaul Floundering Financial District, Economic Cities
headline.print_headline: Saudi to Overhaul Floundering Financial District, Economic Cities

docs.snippet: Saudi Arabia is revising plans for a glitzy financial district in Riyadh and the creation of six industrial cities, after the projects were plagued by delays and a lack of enthusiasm among potential tenants and investors....
